{"title":"蝎子的尾巴及其他","authors":["李学鳌"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":6,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"蝎子的尾巴及其他"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李学鳌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蝎子的尾巴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我没有尾巴！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我没有尾巴！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们为什么不给我插上双翅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫我变为蝴蝶，飞上天哪！？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在阴暗的墙脚下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它拖着蘸满毒液的钩子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拼命地叫喊着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爬！爬！爬！……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“南霸天”的魂灵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“南霸天”的死尸早已腐烂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它的魂灵却留在人间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它咬着铜臭熏绿的牙齿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥着饱饮人民血汗的剑："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我恨！恨！恨！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恨你们夺了我的地盘！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恨你们夺了我的大权！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恨你们共产党无恶不作！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恨你们叫穷小子有了吃穿！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我恨！恨！恨！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它恨人民夺了它的天！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的回答"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不准夺神圣的党的领导权！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不准破坏神圣的社会主义！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们发言！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们发言！！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们用阶级的最强音发言！！！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乘着党整风的台阶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想把我们的队伍搅乱！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打着“爱国”的旗帜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向六亿人民放毒箭！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不准！不准！不准！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你满肚子鬼把戏早被我们看穿！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产党"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——我们的头脑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——我们的心肝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们是历史的发动机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任何诽谤、破坏都无济于事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只能被我们的车轮轧得稀烂！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}